# CLUSTERMAIL

Have you ever opened your email inbox just to be greeted by a seemingly infinite pile of messages? Where's the structure? The order?

Luckily for you, we have the fix: Clustermail! It's an app that provides a natural, graph-based visualization for your email inbox, supporting features like automatic contextual email grouping. With Clustermail, you'll be able to see the same emails as your regular inbox, but with the added bonus of each thread being neatly organized under a relevant label.